title: Episode 221: Lip Service Live Tour Philadelphia (DJ Diamond Kuts, TJ Atoms, Young Chris, Pardison
itunes:title: Episode 221: Lip Service Live Tour Philadelphia (DJ Diamond Kuts, TJ Atoms, Young Chris, Pardison
description:
DJ Diamond Kuts, TJ Atoms, Young Chris, and Pardison Fontaine join the ladies of Lip Service on the first night of the Lip Service Live Tour. What a way to start off the tour...who would've thought the ladies taught Pardi how to apply a tampon. We'd like to give a special thank you to everyone who supported us while we were on the road. We love and appreciate you all. For those who couldn't make it - enjoy!
